- **ODE4J:** Open Dynamics Engine for Java

**2. Autonomous Decision-Making Implementation:**
```java
public class RobotController {
    private PhysicsSpace physicsSpace;
    private RobotAgent robot;

    public void autonomousNavigate() {
        // Sensor data processing
        List<Obstacle> detectedObstacles = robot.scanEnvironment();

        // Decision-making using behavior trees or FSM
